body:
Just wanted to give some love to Riot for adding Icons to each prestige skin. They're also doing it all for no extra expense on our part and I think that's just amazing. I think it'll make owning a prestige skin just a little more substantial as well as letting us show off our little accomplishment without needing to actually use the skin.


Thanks Rito,

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
